    <item>
      <title>The Meaning Of Namaste</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/the-meaning-of-namaste/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/the-meaning-of-namaste/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5094-The-Meaning-Of-Namaste.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Meaning Of Namaste&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Meaning Of Namaste 
    &lt;div id=&#34;the-meaning-of-namaste&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#the-meaning-of-namaste&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“नम्” धातु + ङे प्रत्यय = नम:+ते= नमस्ते  &lt;br&gt;
नम् means bow down  &lt;br&gt;
ते means to you or for you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why should I bow down to you?  &lt;br&gt;
Because you are senior to me?  &lt;br&gt;
Elder to me? More knowledgeable than me?  &lt;br&gt;
Higher in Ashrma to me?  &lt;br&gt;
Wealthier than me?  &lt;br&gt;
Powerful than me?”&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
